default&#xa0;default&#xa0;defaultHizb ut-Tahrirdefault&#xa0;
defaultHizb ut-Tahrir is an Islamist organisation that has a record of offensive and inflammatory statements regarding Jews, non-Muslims, 
defaultand 
defaultgay people
default, amongst others. 
default 
defaultThey 
defaultwere added to the NUS No Platform policy in 2004, which denies them the ability to be involved with the national union. However
default,
default this policy only has an advisory 
defaultcapacity for individual Students’
default Unions. Since then, the organisation has regained 
defaultsome of its p
defaultresence on campus
default via front-groups
